
Installation
------------
Copy the ezcomments extension to your existing eZ Publish installation, then enable it in the Administration Interface (in the Extensions menu under the Setup tab).


Ajax and standard mode
------------
There are two mode in ezcomments. In standard mode, all the request refresh the page. In ajax mode the request will not refresh the entire page.

Change the default view in content to be ajax mode:
In settings/ezcomments.ini
DefaultViewMode=ajax 

Change the default view in content to be standard mode:
DefaultViewMode=standard


Subscrioption activation
-------------
By default it needs activation in subscription process. To disable this feature, 
in settings/ezcomments.ini
SubscriptionActivated=true

